‚ÄéWell, we prepared a gift too.
‚ÄéWhat do you think?

693
00:59:58,011 --> 00:59:59,345
‚ÄéDo you like it?

694
01:00:02,473 --> 01:00:03,391
‚ÄéUncle.

695
01:00:04,350 --> 01:00:05,476
‚ÄéWhat now?

696
01:00:09,439 --> 01:00:10,773
‚ÄéMin-ji.

697
01:00:10,857 --> 01:00:14,485
‚ÄéIf you look to your left behind you,
‚Äéyou'll see an emergency exit.

698
01:00:15,612 --> 01:00:16,946
‚ÄéOn the count of three,

699
01:00:17,655 --> 01:00:20,825
‚ÄéI need you to run that way
‚Äéas fast as you can and don't look back.

700
01:00:21,492 --> 01:00:22,785
‚ÄéWhat are you talking about?

701
01:00:23,453 --> 01:00:25,455
‚Äé-What about you?
‚Äé-Me?

702
01:00:26,414 --> 01:00:29,834
‚ÄéI'm just going to say hi to those men
‚Äéand then catch up with you.

703
01:00:31,294 --> 01:00:33,254
‚ÄéYou can't do this alone.

704
01:00:33,338 --> 01:00:34,422
‚ÄéAll right. One‚Ä¶

705
01:00:35,715 --> 01:00:37,675
‚ÄéYou can shoot Sung Han-soo
‚Äéand claim it was an accident.

706
01:00:37,759 --> 01:00:38,885
‚ÄéDon't kill the girl.

707
01:00:38,968 --> 01:00:40,011
‚ÄéTwo‚Ä¶

708
01:00:40,094 --> 01:00:41,054
‚ÄéUncle!

709
01:00:51,230 --> 01:00:52,857
‚ÄéFire!

710
01:00:52,940 --> 01:00:53,941
‚ÄéThree.

711
01:01:02,075 --> 01:01:03,117
‚ÄéWhat the hell was that?!

712
01:01:06,954 --> 01:01:08,623
‚ÄéHe's always late.

713
01:01:10,917 --> 01:01:12,085
‚ÄéFlashbang.

714
01:01:16,631 --> 01:01:17,465
‚ÄéSmoke grenade.

715
01:01:30,061 --> 01:01:30,895
‚ÄéAttack.

716
01:01:50,790 --> 01:01:51,708
‚ÄéTactical team!

717
01:01:52,458 --> 01:01:54,335
‚ÄéRally at Zone C bunker!

718
01:02:05,263 --> 01:02:06,180
‚ÄéHey, get in!

719
01:02:06,264 --> 01:02:08,599
‚ÄéNice of you to finally show up.

720
01:02:08,683 --> 01:02:10,184
‚ÄéIt's okay, Min-ji.

721
01:02:21,154 --> 01:02:23,072
‚ÄéWhy aren't you getting in? Hurry up!

722
01:02:23,698 --> 01:02:26,033
‚ÄéHow can we get in if the doors won't open?

723
01:02:26,117 --> 01:02:27,577
‚ÄéWhat are we going to do?

724
01:02:38,004 --> 01:02:39,505
‚ÄéDamn it.

725
01:02:41,591 --> 01:02:42,759
‚ÄéYou're shooting blanks, aren't you?

726
01:02:47,889 --> 01:02:48,931
‚ÄéThey're blank rounds.

727
01:02:50,892 --> 01:02:51,851
‚ÄéHey, take cover!

728
01:02:53,561 --> 01:02:54,645
‚ÄéThey're blank rounds! Fire!

729
01:02:56,272 --> 01:02:57,398
‚ÄéHey, Min-ji!

730
01:02:58,524 --> 01:03:01,235
‚ÄéOh, for crying out loud! My car!

731
01:03:03,696 --> 01:03:06,157
‚ÄéHey, you should've brought some live ammo!

732
01:03:06,240 --> 01:03:08,785
‚ÄéWhy did you bring all blank rounds?

733
01:03:08,868 --> 01:03:10,161
‚ÄéThey caught on right away.

734
01:03:10,244 --> 01:03:12,163
‚ÄéI did bring live ammo!

735
01:03:12,246 --> 01:03:14,665
‚ÄéBut I can't go around
‚Äékilling my juniors, can I?

736
01:03:18,127 --> 01:03:19,796
‚ÄéJeez, my car, man!

737
01:03:28,179 --> 01:03:29,347
‚ÄéThis won't do, huh?

738
01:03:30,223 --> 01:03:31,057
‚ÄéHere.

739
01:03:33,100 --> 01:03:33,935
‚ÄéChoose one!

740
01:03:35,061 --> 01:03:37,939
‚ÄéI can't choose
‚Äébecause I love both of them!

741
01:03:38,022 --> 01:03:40,024
‚Äé-Choose one.
‚Äé-You want to have a shootout?

742
01:03:42,068 --> 01:03:43,236
‚ÄéHold your fire!

743
01:03:55,331 --> 01:03:56,499
‚ÄéHey, Park Jin-cheol.

744
01:03:57,625 --> 01:03:58,459
‚ÄéNow what?

745
01:03:59,126 --> 01:04:00,253
‚ÄéYou want us to continue?

746
01:04:12,014 --> 01:04:13,558
‚ÄéThis is a white flag.

747
01:04:13,641 --> 01:04:14,475
‚ÄéWe surrender!

748
01:04:15,184 --> 01:04:16,644
‚ÄéWe're coming out, so don't shoot!

749
01:04:18,855 --> 01:04:19,814
‚ÄéWe're coming!

750
01:04:21,399 --> 01:04:22,525
‚ÄéNice and slow!

751
01:04:23,609 --> 01:04:24,777
‚ÄéSlowly!

752
01:04:24,861 --> 01:04:26,112
‚ÄéSlowly!

753
01:04:26,696 --> 01:04:27,905
‚ÄéWhy are there so many of you?

754
01:04:28,531 --> 01:04:30,533
‚ÄéAll of you just to catch the three of us?

755
01:04:33,953 --> 01:04:36,789
‚ÄéI saved you from drowning,
‚Äéand you shoot live ammo?

756
01:04:37,415 --> 01:04:39,166
‚ÄéThere's a kid here too, you mole rat.

757
01:04:39,250 --> 01:04:42,753
‚ÄéYou return to your old stomping grounds
‚Äéafter all this time, wreck the place,

758
01:04:42,837 --> 01:04:43,713
‚Äéand expect me to sit back?

759
01:04:44,630 --> 01:04:45,464
‚ÄéTake her.

760
01:04:45,548 --> 01:04:46,674
‚Äé-Yes, sir.
‚Äé-Yes, sir.

761
01:04:48,384 --> 01:04:49,427
‚ÄéAll of you!

762
01:04:50,511 --> 01:04:51,387
‚ÄéDrop your guns!

763
01:05:01,981 --> 01:05:02,940
‚ÄéWhat are you doing?

764
01:05:04,233 --> 01:05:05,943
‚ÄéI said drop your guns!

765
01:05:53,699 --> 01:05:54,784
‚ÄéDad?

766
01:06:06,671 --> 01:06:07,797
‚ÄéDad!

767
01:06:07,880 --> 01:06:08,881
‚ÄéWait here.

768
01:06:11,384 --> 01:06:12,218
‚ÄéMin-ji.

769
01:06:14,553 --> 01:06:15,638
‚ÄéI'm here.

770
01:06:22,061 --> 01:06:23,229
‚ÄéLet's go home now.

771
01:06:23,813 --> 01:06:24,814
‚ÄéDad‚Ä¶

772
01:07:08,149 --> 01:07:11,861
‚ÄéAGENT KIM REACTIVATED

773
01:07:13,446 --> 01:07:15,740
‚ÄéI'm here now, so don't worry.

774
01:07:18,367 --> 01:07:20,369
‚ÄéI'm going to witness the end myself.

775
01:07:20,453 --> 01:07:22,329
‚ÄéJust take a quick nap, hero!

776
01:07:23,330 --> 01:07:26,042
‚ÄéAn attempted cover-up and a kidnapping‚Ä¶

777
01:07:26,125 --> 01:07:28,753
‚ÄéWe should take this chance
‚Äéto get rid of him first.

778
01:07:28,836 --> 01:07:30,421
‚ÄéI'm sure you weren't
‚Äéin your right mind either,

779
01:07:30,504 --> 01:07:31,839
‚Äétrying to find your daughter.

780
01:07:31,922 --> 01:07:35,176
‚ÄéToday will be the last time
‚ÄéAgent Kim sees Min-ji.

781
01:07:36,010 --> 01:07:37,094
‚ÄéDad!

782
01:07:39,597 --> 01:07:41,265
‚ÄéFor Min-ji's sake,

783
01:07:41,348 --> 01:07:42,516
‚ÄéI'm going to

784
01:07:42,600 --> 01:07:43,726
‚Äéend you.

785
01:07:45,978 --> 01:07:48,898
‚ÄéSubtitle translation by: Jenny Kim
